review_content:
I've started to use Boursorama bank in France 4 weeks ago. Everything seems to be great:
 - the debit card works fine; 
 - the check book was delivered by mail as promised;
 - no problems with the internet payments;
 - no problems with the use of the card in stores or shops.

Completely free. No fees whatsoever.
I did not try the other services yet. 

I have recently moved to France.
